reviewText: This video movie is not intended to teach people how to fix the hybrid car especially to repair or recondition its hybrid battery. It is just informative how thoroughly the car hybrid system works especially for Toyota Prius and a little bit for Honda Insight.
I found the information very useful and it is always nice to be able to review material and have somewhere to reference for information.  For the price you can't beat it.

This video shows easy-to-understand explanation of how hybrid system works by nice illustrative animation.
I can further delve into the mystery of world's most advanced automotive mechanism.
Good for beignners. Basic information is provided. Not bad , not good. that is why i gave 3 star. But worth for money.
